title: Watch: Code Kunst Releases “Fire Water” Music Video Featuring G.Soul And Tablo
text:
Pin Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
YG Entertainment has released the music video for Code Kunst’s new track “Fire Water” featuring G.Soul and Epik High’s Tablo ! 
As the name of the song might suggest, the music video turns the peculiar idea of fire and water coexisting into a reality. Some of the scenes show the starring actors and singers standing on a platform surrounded by water, while the poles around them are lit on fire, creating an eerily contrasting atmosphere. 
Code Kunst is signed under YG Entertainment’s sub-label HIGHGRND, which was founded by Tablo. Meanwhile, G.Soul is a singer-songwriter at JYP Entertainment.
